Commentary Text: Ashwin to Rahane, out Caught by Buttler!! Ashwin wins his battle against Rahane again. That's 6th time in the IPL and twice this season. CSK losing wickets in consecutive overs and that brings two new batters at the crease. RR well on top. Rahane comes down the track, gets a bit too close to the carrom ball and hence does not get the elevation to clear long-on, Buttler runs to his right and takes a good catch. Commentary Text: Zampa to Gaikwad, out Caught by Padikkal!! Big wicket for RR. The set batter goes. Simple stuff from Zamps. Bowls the leggie within the stumps to force the right-handers to target the leg-side and play across the line. Commentary Text: Zampa to Conway, out Caught by Sandeep Sharma!! This was coming. Brilliant captaincy from Sanju Samson. Pressure over for CSK and he brought on a smart white ball operator. Yeah, I am dangling a legbreak outside off stump in the slot to see what you can do kind of ball from Zampa. Conway thought he could take the aerial route over the infield, but smashed this straight to mid-off and Zampa is thrilled. Conway struggled to get going today. RR have won the powerplay battle. Conway c Sandeep Sharma b Zampa 8(16) [4s-1]
